<subSubSection pageId="11" pageNumber="78" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph pageId="11" pageNumber="78">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="11" pageNumber="78">
Adult (
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 3–12" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 3 - 12. Habitus of Herpetogramma species 3, 4 H. biconvexa sp. nov. 3 male, holotype 4 female, paratype 5, 6 H. rudis 5 male 6 female 7, 8 H. longispina sp. nov. 7 male, holotype 8 female, paratype 9, 10 H. brachyacantha sp. nov. 9 male, holotype 10 female, paratype 11, 12 H. magna 11 male 12 female." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.865.35111.figures3-12" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/319052" pageId="11" pageNumber="78">Figs 11</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 3–12" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 3 - 12. Habitus of Herpetogramma species 3, 4 H. biconvexa sp. nov. 3 male, holotype 4 female, paratype 5, 6 H. rudis 5 male 6 female 7, 8 H. longispina sp. nov. 7 male, holotype 8 female, paratype 9, 10 H. brachyacantha sp. nov. 9 male, holotype 10 female, paratype 11, 12 H. magna 11 male 12 female." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.865.35111.figures3-12" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/319052" pageId="11" pageNumber="78">12</figureCitation>
): Wings brown or dark brown tinged with faint yellow, lines and spots dark brown. Forewing with faint yellow between orbicular spot and discoidal spot, postmedial line excurved and pointedly serrated from M1 to CuA2, adjoined by a serrated light-yellow line outside. Male genitalia (
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 21–35" captionStartId="F5" captionText="Figures 21 - 35. Genitalia of Herpetogramma species. 21 - 25 H. longispina sp. nov.: 21 - 23 male, holotype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17418 24, 25 female, paratype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17370 26 - 30 H. brachyacantha sp. nov.: 26 - 28 male, holotype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17421 29, 30 female, paratype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17379 31 - 35 H. magna: 31 - 33 male, genitalia slide no. WJP 17423 34, 35 female, genitalia slide no. WJP 17416 22, 27, 32 lamellate protuberance on base of valva 23, 28, 33 cornuti in male genitalia 25, 30, 35 signum of female genitalia." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.865.35111.figures21-35" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/319054" pageId="11" pageNumber="78">Figs 31-33</figureCitation>
): Uncus narrowed, distal 1/3 bearing dorsal setae, apex pointed. Valva subfusiform, densely ciliated and bearing a lamellate basal projection (
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 21–35" captionStartId="F5" captionText="Figures 21 - 35. Genitalia of Herpetogramma species. 21 - 25 H. longispina sp. nov.: 21 - 23 male, holotype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17418 24, 25 female, paratype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17370 26 - 30 H. brachyacantha sp. nov.: 26 - 28 male, holotype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17421 29, 30 female, paratype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17379 31 - 35 H. magna: 31 - 33 male, genitalia slide no. WJP 17423 34, 35 female, genitalia slide no. WJP 17416 22, 27, 32 lamellate protuberance on base of valva 23, 28, 33 cornuti in male genitalia 25, 30, 35 signum of female genitalia." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.865.35111.figures21-35" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/319054" pageId="11" pageNumber="78">Fig. 32</figureCitation>
). Phallus with a cluster of long spinose cornuti gathered to subfusiform, ca. 1/4 the length of the phallus (
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 21–35" captionStartId="F5" captionText="Figures 21 - 35. Genitalia of Herpetogramma species. 21 - 25 H. longispina sp. nov.: 21 - 23 male, holotype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17418 24, 25 female, paratype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17370 26 - 30 H. brachyacantha sp. nov.: 26 - 28 male, holotype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17421 29, 30 female, paratype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17379 31 - 35 H. magna: 31 - 33 male, genitalia slide no. WJP 17423 34, 35 female, genitalia slide no. WJP 17416 22, 27, 32 lamellate protuberance on base of valva 23, 28, 33 cornuti in male genitalia 25, 30, 35 signum of female genitalia." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.865.35111.figures21-35" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/319054" pageId="11" pageNumber="78">Fig. 33</figureCitation>
). Female genitalia (
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 21–35" captionStartId="F5" captionText="Figures 21 - 35. Genitalia of Herpetogramma species. 21 - 25 H. longispina sp. nov.: 21 - 23 male, holotype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17418 24, 25 female, paratype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17370 26 - 30 H. brachyacantha sp. nov.: 26 - 28 male, holotype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17421 29, 30 female, paratype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17379 31 - 35 H. magna: 31 - 33 male, genitalia slide no. WJP 17423 34, 35 female, genitalia slide no. WJP 17416 22, 27, 32 lamellate protuberance on base of valva 23, 28, 33 cornuti in male genitalia 25, 30, 35 signum of female genitalia." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.865.35111.figures21-35" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/319054" pageId="11" pageNumber="78">Figs 34</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 21–35" captionStartId="F5" captionText="Figures 21 - 35. Genitalia of Herpetogramma species. 21 - 25 H. longispina sp. nov.: 21 - 23 male, holotype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17418 24, 25 female, paratype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17370 26 - 30 H. brachyacantha sp. nov.: 26 - 28 male, holotype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17421 29, 30 female, paratype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17379 31 - 35 H. magna: 31 - 33 male, genitalia slide no. WJP 17423 34, 35 female, genitalia slide no. WJP 17416 22, 27, 32 lamellate protuberance on base of valva 23, 28, 33 cornuti in male genitalia 25, 30, 35 signum of female genitalia." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.865.35111.figures21-35" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/319054" pageId="11" pageNumber="78">35</figureCitation>
): Corpus bursae nearly pear-shaped. Signum nearly square, slightly depressed along diagonal axis (
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 21–35" captionStartId="F5" captionText="Figures 21 - 35. Genitalia of Herpetogramma species. 21 - 25 H. longispina sp. nov.: 21 - 23 male, holotype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17418 24, 25 female, paratype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17370 26 - 30 H. brachyacantha sp. nov.: 26 - 28 male, holotype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17421 29, 30 female, paratype, genitalia slide no. WJP 17379 31 - 35 H. magna: 31 - 33 male, genitalia slide no. WJP 17423 34, 35 female, genitalia slide no. WJP 17416 22, 27, 32 lamellate protuberance on base of valva 23, 28, 33 cornuti in male genitalia 25, 30, 35 signum of female genitalia." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.865.35111.figures21-35" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/319054" pageId="11" pageNumber="78">Fig. 35</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
